# Royal Mix Global – Domain Verification Guide

## TXT Record Setup
Host/Name: _pi-domain-verification
Value: c...dc73f
TTL: 300 (5 min)
Add this TXT record to your DNS provider.

## HTTPS Requirement
Make sure https://royalmixinternational.com has a valid SSL certificate.

## Verification Steps
1. Go to Pi Developers Dashboard
2. Enter your domain: royalmixinternational.com
3. Click Verify Domain
4. If TXT record is correctly propagated, verification completes within 30–60 seconds

## DNS Propagation Check
Use https://www.whatsmydns.net/ to check TXT propagation globally.

## Pi SDK Callback Example
```javascript
const piSDK = require('pi-sdk');

piSDK.verifyDomain({
  domain: 'royalmixinternational.com',
  key: 'cefc3ac44cdbbea470881534ced3b575e61706a7310cd2a60fc242553d9a198c8588944b7df8352ac4806bb89f8584b86c439bd1fcbb1c789e154ce3cb3dc73f'
});
